channel.title: Compile Doesn't work with Java! please need help
channel.description:

"You do not have JDk 6.0 or JDK 5.0 or any 6.0 or 5.0 updates. Go to mod Taharoks tutorial on the Moparscape tutorial section for step by step instructions on how to download them"
Ok to start off with i have: JDK 6 Update 4, JDK 6 Update 2, and JDK 5. i also couldn't find mod Taharoks tut.
So if anyone out there can help me with this problem it would be great.
Thanks, Baller50
